# Form for Course Creation and Edit in Admin Dashboard

## Depiction of the page

The page should have this fields. The data would be sent as a FormData by the frontend project

### Fields

- title: required
- slug: required
- description: required
- thumbnail url: required

## Actions

- Create, fix, and maintain the course creation, update, and deletion logic in `CourseController`. Don't forget to keep the controller lean. Utilize the `Services` and `Repositories`
- Validate the request body with the Laravel Request validation feature, before proceeding with any query and mutation
